## ðŸ›  Troubleshooting

**Record not found**  
â†’ Wrong FormID or plugin name  

**No valid items found**  
â†’ Outfit group empty or incorrect  

**NPC outfit unchanged**  
â†’ Requires new game or `recycleactor`

